name: figure 1
description: This is one of the artworks of the collection of figures that I drawing manually with pencil and conte and editing in software finally. In this collection, I drawing figures expressive manner and I am intensifying it by editing in software. I want to show their inner life and mental tensions. I really enjoy hand drawing and I can focus on different aspects of my subject. I intend to expand such artwork over time and to show how much artistic potential there is in this kind of approach.
